Package: multiai
Version: 0.0.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Laurent Rochetta <laurent@rochetta.fr>
Homepage: https://rochetta.fr
Description: Route multiple AI CLIs with isolated env profiles
 multiai is a command-line tool that routes between multiple AI CLIs
 (Claude Code, Codex CLI, OpenCode) using isolated environment profiles.
 It provides a unified interface for launching different AI tools
 with provider-specific API keys and configuration.
